data.description:
A 4/3 stick built home on 5.31 acres, would make an awesome hunt club deer galore.
Recently painted exterior, and interior.
Built 2008, not lakeside, but accessible multiple areas of the lake. Desired East Lake Sinclair GA
Outside shed for tools and covered parking.
Over 90% land is cleared, bring your ATV sport fan perfect place for all.
This property is Not being rented, owner is selling only. That said please don’t call to ask if it can be rented for any short or long term.

Will pay 3% to selling agent who brings buyer Gorgeous turn key 5.31 acre property on East Lake Sinclair in historic Hancock County Georgia.
 Home just newly painted, RV pad on property. Bring your ATV’S lot’s of property, trails to ride on.
Fantastic AirBNB opportunity for the Investor. 
Owner has created a 4 Wheeler tract for fun. 
The tract would make a fantastic AirBNB attraction. 

There is a separate power pole & water connection on roughly .71 acres of the 5.31 acres total. 

Property would make a awesome 2nd home for the large families who want to get away for privacy or a beautiful forever home! 

Home is Private Property. Do Not Disturb Owners. 
Contact Us to schedule a private showing.
